#NewlineHOUSE RULES:
#Newline- Dealer must draw to 17
#Newline- Blackjack pays 3 for 2 (rounded up to the nearest coin)
#Newline- Maximum bet is 10 coins
#Newline- The game ends when you either lose all your coins or break the bank by making 250 coins

Good luck!
